title: The best place to live in Kent here @Signature Pointe!
posting_body: ['25102 62nd Ave S, Kent, WA 98032', 'Our resort-style community embodies all the elements necessary for great apartment living.', 'From our unique architecture and spacious floor plans, to our state-of-the-art recreation pavilion, you will love calling Signature Pointe your new home!', 'Call now and schedule a tour appointment!', 'Apartment Features:', 'Full-Size Washer/Dryer', 'Built-In Bookshelves', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Double Sinks', 'Top Floor Units Feature 19-ft Ceilings', 'Microwave', 'Community Features:', 'Close to Schools, Restaurants, & Shops', 'Adjacent to Riverbend Golf Course', 'Heated Indoor Pool, Sauna, & Spa', 'Garages & Carports Available', 'Basketball & Tennis Courts', 'Zero Deposit Options Available', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs Allowed', 'Limit 2 Pets Per Home', '1 Pet: $20 Pet Rent per month', '1 Pet: $200 Pet Deposit (Refundable)', '1 Pet: $300 Pet Fee (Non-Refundable)', 'Additional Pets Fee: $100/ Pet (Non-Refundable)', 'Breed Restrictions May Apply', 'Minimum Age Limit May Apply', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 9am - 6pm', 'Tuesday: 9am - 6pm', 'Wednesday: 9am - 6pm', 'Thursday: 9am - 6pm', 'Friday: 9am - 6pm', 'Saturday: 9am - 5:30pm', 'Sunday: 9am - 5:30pm', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
